 明既直接送去支那打靶. 老婆同女任雜種強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T10:54:43.000Z","msg":"Agger"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"港豬: 我們最幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086afa6595ddbc3b7e8f5479bd450d6d15eb9f41","tid":1091303,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4382c4b161a60a47d731f48710c34e33311ec6ab","tid":1091303,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77f519e84e2b37bf5b2bfb3e63e39cd2c9c5385d","tid":1091303,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b62af48879ed2c1f9c43059c63c82e3f2a3805ca","tid":1091303,"uid":126731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"香港人唔使明, 明既直接送去支那打靶. 老婆同女任雜種強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T10:54:43.000Z","msg":"Agger"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"港豬: 我們最幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"睇到篇文都睇到眼濕濕"},{"pid":"528b68490c791bfe7ac4380b3a6e1157f9700ddb","tid":1091303,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:54:11.000Z","msg":"美國佬見到真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e092719bbc33caf4ca50a16348da45afe024b9fd","tid":1091303,"uid":126412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:55:32.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"96384af04ed546f0f947090c40cc149871cfad39","tid":1091303,"uid":169154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:58:56.000Z","msg":"老兵望見呢一代既台灣人應該嘔血"},{"pid":"3f5450040cb8130f62ab0cc97353e3f1eae9f925","tid":1091303,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T23:54:25.000Z","msg":"比著香港人，實嚇到瀨屎"},{"pid":"69bde713a484d56899654e0053f9f9a40e77e7c9","tid":1091303,"uid":101051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T00:31:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/193725958489/posts/10156980148533490/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F193725958489%2Fposts%2F10156980148533490%2F&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvBURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=a8d0d4ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/193725958489/posts/10156980148533490/</a><br />\n<br />\n感謝有美國做後盾！剛好那時我在中部竹仔坑陸軍裝甲獨立第73旅當兵，那時叫「華山操演」，戰備提昇到3級「準戰爭狀態」準備和共匪一搏，旅上能動的戰甲砲車，和各式輪型車輛共700台全部傾巢而出備戰，當第一台戰車已抵達台中港，最後一台砲車還未出營區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讚，晚半年剛好閃過，不然那一個月全旅到旅集合場檢查個人大裝備（準備打仗了），除了睡覺可脫鋼盔外，連到營餐廳吃飯，都是全副武裝槍不離身！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每一個在那段時期服過兵役的,都難忘那種肅殺跟風雨欲來的氣氛! 我是1994 退伍的,那時也有心理準備會隨時被叫回去<br />\n<br />\n那年本部隊剛從嘉義將軍山下完基地，一個多月後，任務編組一個戰車排前進支援東莒島，登島第一件事就是寫遺書交由政戰官保管，而整個東莒島百姓全跑光了，只剩下完成作戰準備的阿兵哥，島上指揮官改由馬防部來的一位少將坐鎮指揮。"}]}